eld developers to add support for WPAI to their field types</li>\n<li>bug fix: import repeater field generated with PHP didn\'t work</li>\n<li>bug fix: import ACF local fields didn\'t work in some cases</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3.3.0</p>\n<ul>\n<li>bug fix: Date picker used wrong format</li>\n<li>bug fix: Import template showing empty values for repeater fields</li>\n<li>bug fix: Link field inside fixed repeater field was not imported correctly</li>\n<li>bug fix: Nested taxonomy fields were not rendered correctly in import template</li>\n<li>bug fix: the ACF Field groups weren\'t chosen correctly when import bundle from WP All Export</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3.2.9</p>\n<ul>\n<li>improvement: add support for table field</li>\n<li>improvement: check post types when searching by ID for relationship fields</li>\n<li>bug fix: UI broken for True False field</li>\n<li>bug fix: \'Select value for all records\' not working for \'Taxonomy\' fields</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3.2.8</p>\n<ul>\n<li>improvement: compatibility with WordPress 5.5</li>\n<li>bug fix: import taxonomies inside repeater doesn\'t work in same cases</li>\n<li>bug fix: WYSIWYG field data prefixed with space</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3.2.7</p>\n<ul>\n<li>bug fix: Multiple Select field not imported correctly</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3.2.6</p>\n<ul>\n<li>improvement: add default zoom value for Google Maps field</li>\n<li>API: apply pmxi_acf_custom_field filter to taxonomy terms meta</li>\n<li>bug fix: unable to double click to insert XPath in some cases</li>\n<li>bug fix: unable to import WooCommerce customer ACF fields</li>\n<li>bug fix: select field with stylized UI not rendered properly</li>\n<li>bug fix: empty layouts for Flexible Content fields improperly imported</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3.2.5</p>\n<ul>\n<li>improvement: extend Google Maps field options</li>\n<li>improvement: save custom choice for radio button field</li>\n<li>bug fix: Google Maps field UI does not render properly</li>\n<li>bug fix: unable to import country field with multiple values</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3.2.4</p>\n<ul>\n<li>improvement: add support for Image Aspect Ratio Crop field</li>\n<li>bug fix: unable to add new images to gallery field</li>\n<li>bug fix: unable to add link field inside repeater</li>\n<li>bug fix: group field not rendering properly</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3.2.3</p>\n<ul>\n<li>bug fix: import gallery field inside repeater produced set of duplicate rows</li>\n<li>bug fix: import ACF field key was populated with field name instead of field key</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3.2.2- Fixed import repeater field3.2.1</p>\n<ul>\n<li>improvement: add support for country field - https://github.com/nlemoine/acf-country</li>\n<li>improvement: apply ACF filters when importing field values</li>\n<li>bug fix:search existing images by filename doesn\'t work correctly with galleries</li>\n<li>bug fix: $articleData argument missing in wp_all_import_images_uploads_dir filter</li>\n<li>bug fix: taxonomy field for users not importing properly</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3.2.0</p>\n<ul>\n<li>improvement: added support for new ACF field: Star Rating</li>\n<li>bug fix: compatibility with ACF v5.7.11</li>\n<li>bug fix: compatibility with ACF v4.4.12</li>\n<li>bug fix: rendering select field choices</li>\n<li>bug fix: search for existing images option</li>\n<li>bug fix: rendering ACF groups</li>\n<li>bug fix: Google Map field - save lat and long as string instead of decimal value</li>\n<li>bug fix: import taxonomy field inside repeater in fixed mode</li>\n<li>bug fix: import empty checkbox field</li>\n<li>bug fix: import repeater in XML mode</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3.1.9</p>\n<ul>\n<li>bug fix: ACF groups visibility on import template screen</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3.1.8</p>\n<ul>\n<li>improvement: render only visible ACF field groups on import template screen</li>\n<li>improvement: added new field support - image_crop</li>\n<li>bug fix: import Relationship field</li>\n<li>bug fix: import taxonomy hierarchy inside Repeater</li>\n<li>bug fix: ignore empty rows for Repeater in csv mode</li>\n<li>bug fix: import checkbox using XPath</li>\n<li>bug fix: import post object field with multiple selection</li>\n<li>bug fix: import Repeater inside Repeater in csv mode</li>\n<li>bug fix: ignore empty rows option</li>\n<li>bug fix: detecting google map api key</li>\n<li>bug fix: date format for date picker field ACF 4.x</li>\n<li>bug fix: update only these fields for ACF 4.x</li>\n<li>bug fix: rendering local ACF fields defined in ACF 4.x syntax</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3.1.7</p>\n<ul>\n<li>bug fix: import nested repeaters in XML mode</li>\n<li>bug fix: \'Ignore empty rows\' doesn\'t ignore empty rows</li>\n<li>bug fix: repeater sub fields not saved in ACF 4.x</li>\n<li>bug fix: unable to set relationship fields when post type is not defined for related content</li>\n<li>bug fix: unable to import taxonomy fields inside repeater fields</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3.1.6</p>\n<ul>\n<li>improvement: added support for link field</li>\n<li>improvement: added support for Font Awesome Icon field</li>\n<li>improvement: added support for range field</li>\n<li>improvement: added support for button_group field</li>\n<li>improvement: render acf groups alphabetically</li>\n<li>bug fix: import post object filed based on acf post type settings</li>\n<li>bug fix: updating acf when update option disabled</li>\n<li>bug fix: added wp_all_import_images_uploads_dir filter</li>\n<li>bug fix: rendering ACF local fields</li>\n<li>bug fix: import relationship field based on custom types in field settings</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3.1.5</p>\n<ul>\n<li>bug fix: import post object field</li>\n<li>bug fix: matching relationship posts</li>\n<li>bug fix: using google maps api key</li>\n<li>bug fix: import clone group field</li>\n<li>bug fix: date time picker format</li>\n<li>bug fix: import empty image field in repeater</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3.1.4</p>\n<ul>\n<li>improvement: performance optimization</li>\n<li>improvement: added support for Vimeo field type</li>\n<li>bug fix: search for existing files</li>\n<li>bug fix: import images into File field</li